  "Description": "MODIFICATIONS:\n\nDEVELOPER            DATE                 PROJECT          DESCRIPTION                                   ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW DATE\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  \n-----------------------------     ----------------------     --------------------        ---------------------------------------------            -------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\nLeandrew Moore       06/06/2013         5114                    rewrite in parallel                               Enterprisewarehouse    Jag Yelavarthi             2013-08-27  \nSantosh Bokka         05/15/2014         TFS 2363    Added 2 columns CRT_RUN_CYC_EXCTN_SK \n                                                                                 and LAST_UPDT_RUN_CYC_EXCTN_SK    EnterpriseNewDevl    Kalyan Neelam          2014-05-23\n\nAnnotations:\nJob IdsEdwProvCatD Load.\nRead the Load ready file created in Extract job or PKEY job\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file\n\nThis file is an append\nLoad file created in the previous job will be loaded into the target DB2 table here. \n\nUpdate logic; \"Update then Insert\" Or \"Insert then Update\" will be chosen depending on the nature of data going into the table. If there are more updates than Inserts, then Update then Insert should be selected.\nWhen the Inserts are more than Updates, then Insert then Update should be selected"
